  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985620/extras/53683d88c15080248cfc56cb58e23887.avif?t=1724864567\" width=500 height=286 /></span><br><br>This is a pure love Adventure Game<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985620/extras/e79a53fe475cfa9e1dcc96f46a89106d.webp?t=1724864567\" width=522 height=47 /></span><br>Players unfold the story from Moffts' point of view.<br>In the dark night at the office, Mofft is gradually overwhelmed by the reality of his grave mistake. <br>The loss of life, everything, as if the world had abandoned this woman──Lasling stands quietly at the end of the corridor.<br>Though the two sides are constantly entangled by the past, they turn out to be each other's redemption.\t<br><br>\"If that accident hadn't happened, would I still have met you?\"<br>\"Even if everything about me is falling apart, would you still stay by my side?\"<br>\"In the mountain at the back of the company, she still waits for me under the cypress tree.\"<br>\"Even now, faults and mistakes are still blaming me.\"<br>\"Will you be able to find happiness just by going to the far south?\"<br><br>Now, let's indulge in this bitter and unforgettable love together<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985620/extras/35abdd050203c6f96a53fe8c8697d6d9.webp?t=1724864567\" width=522 height=47 /></span><br><br>Game contents:<br>ASMR voice<br>50 basic CGs<br>Check out heroines in different outfits<br>Deep and touching pure love story<br>20+ original soundtracks<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985620/extras/d7e221486a6ffda6907645db997620cf.poster.avif?t=1724864567\" widt